---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Crowns & Bridges" 
  category="Restorative Dentistry"
  description="Restore damaged teeth with crowns or replace missing teeth with bridges. On-site fabrication for single appointment completion."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598256989800-fe5f95da9787?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Complete Tooth Restoration</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Crowns protect broken or weakened teeth, while bridges replace missing teeth. 
        With our on-site fabrication equipment, many restorations can be completed in a single appointment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Dental Crowns -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Dental Crowns</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            A crown is a cap that completely covers a damaged, cracked, or severely decayed tooth. 
            It restores the tooth's shape, size, strength, and appearance.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">When You Need a Crown:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            <li>• Large cavity that's too big for a filling</li>
            <li>• Cracked or broken tooth</li>
            <li>• Tooth weakened by root canal treatment</li>
            <li>• Severe tooth wear or grinding damage</li>
            <li>• Cosmetic improvement of misshapen teeth</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Dental Bridges -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Dental Bridges</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            A bridge literally bridges the gap created by one or more missing teeth. 
            It consists of crowns on adjacent teeth with a replacement tooth in between.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Benefits of Bridges:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">
            <li>• Restore your ability to chew and speak properly</li>
            <li>• Maintain facial shape and prevent sagging</li>
            <li>• Prevent remaining teeth from shifting</li>
            <li>• Distribute bite forces evenly</li>
            <li>• Restore your confident smile</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Crown & Bridge Materials
    </h2>

    <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Porcelain -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">All-Porcelain/Ceramic</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Advantages:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Most natural-looking option</li>
              <li>• Excellent color matching</li>
              <li>• Metal-free and biocompatible</li>
              <li>• No dark lines at the gum</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Best For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Front teeth (highly visible areas)</li>
              <li>• Patients with metal allergies</li>
              <li>• Those wanting the most natural appearance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Porcelain-fused-to-metal -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-3">Porcelain-Fused-to-Metal (PFM)</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Advantages:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Strong and durable</li>
              <li>• Good aesthetics</li>
              <li>• Proven track record</li>
              <li>• Cost-effective option</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Best For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Back teeth (heavy chewing forces)</li>
              <li>• Long-span bridges</li>
              <li>• Budget-conscious patients</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Gold -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-50 to-yellow-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-3">Gold Alloy</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Advantages:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Extremely durable and long-lasting</li>
              <li>• Gentle on opposing teeth</li>
              <li>• Precise fit</li>
              <li>• Biocompatible</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Best For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Back teeth (not visible when smiling)</li>
              <li>• Patients who grind their teeth</li>
              <li>• Maximum longevity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Treatment Process
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Traditional Process (2 visits)</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white text-sm font-bold">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Preparation & Impressions</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Tooth preparation, impressions, temporary crown</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-white text-sm font-bold">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Final Placement</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Remove temporary, place permanent crown/bridge (2-3 weeks later)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">CEREC Same-Day (1 visit)</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-primary-900 text-sm font-bold">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Digital Preparation</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Tooth preparation and digital scanning</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-primary-900 text-sm font-bold">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Design & Mill</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Computer design and in-office milling</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-primary-900 text-sm font-bold">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Immediate Placement</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Placement and final adjustments (same day!)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Caring for Your Crown or Bridge
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Daily Care</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Brush twice daily with fluoride toothpaste</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Floss daily (special floss threaders for bridges)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Use an antimicrobial mouthwash</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Regular dental checkups every 6 months</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Avoid</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Chewing ice, hard candy, or nuts</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Using teeth as tools to open packages</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Grinding or clenching teeth (wear a night guard)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Sticky foods that can pull off crowns</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Restore Your Smile's Function & Beauty
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Don't let damaged or missing teeth compromise your oral health and confidence. 
        Our crowns and bridges provide long-lasting solutions that look and feel natural.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/cerec" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">CEREC Same-Day Crowns</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Get crowns in one appointment</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/dental-restoration" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Implants</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Permanent tooth replacement</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/root-canal" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Root Canal Therapy</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Save severely damaged teeth</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long do crowns and bridges last?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        With proper care, dental crowns typically last 10-15 years, while bridges can last 10-20 years. 
        Factors like oral hygiene, eating habits, and regular dental visits significantly impact longevity.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Will my crown or bridge look natural?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Absolutely! We carefully match the color, shape, and size of your crowns and bridges to your 
        natural teeth. Modern materials like all-ceramic crowns are virtually indistinguishable from 
        natural teeth.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Is the crown procedure painful?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        We use local anesthesia to ensure you're comfortable during the procedure. Some sensitivity 
        is normal for a few days after treatment, but most patients experience minimal discomfort 
        that's easily managed with over-the-counter pain relievers.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">What's the difference between a crown and a bridge?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        A crown covers and protects a single damaged tooth. A bridge replaces one or more missing 
        teeth by connecting crowns on adjacent teeth with replacement teeth in between. Both restore 
        function and appearance.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>